    <!-- Privacy and Permissions -->
    <string name="privacy_policy">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_agreement_title">Privacy Agreement</string>
    <string name="privacy_agreement_content">This application collects motion sensor data and redacted UI component context for academic research.\n\n• Sensors: accelerometer, gyroscope, and magnetic field.\n\n• Accessibility: reads accessible component structure and allowed fields only. It does not click, type, perform gestures, capture screenshots, or record keystrokes.\n\n• Text privacy: raw input field text is dropped, password nodes are dropped, and fixed-format sensitive strings are redacted before upload.\n\n• Transport: redacted data is serialized as JSON, compressed with LZ4 frame, and uploaded through HTTPS/TLS in deployment. This research stage does not use content AES encryption.\n\n• Screen state: collection stops while the screen is off or locked.\n\nBy continuing, you consent to this data collection and processing.</string>
